r />\n唔係一碌鳩打成船人，但我身邊真係冇樓主所講嘅例子（自觀覺得有都係佔極少數，eg讀獸醫/香港冇嘅專科）"},{"pid":"61749859735e5246903a933ae5f46336d2af61df","tid":611710,"uid":712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"根本去台灣讀垃圾科個d就係又冇家底又唔肯接受現實既垃圾"},{"pid":"bded0a726273dc8c580de343bc97eb76c683c918","tid":611710,"uid":28535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"台大校友揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7171279bc62b947b25d702eeafd85372a158ae","tid":611710,"uid":46504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"屌你10幾分出國係要讀foundation 再駁入大學架 你估直入呀 邊撚度夠班呀"},{"pid":"140bca301fd6ca9138792968c025fde77ff12517","tid":611710,"uid":177247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"有冇食台妹先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4656b390cf8de6c165b6326373700bf5c5c7e384","tid":611710,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"去越南泰國讀仲有著數過去台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b79655181ce7f970edae0cf24eb6986dc621c","tid":611710,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8f8760c97399939b2de7f743b7f1dc8dea0465","tid":611710,"uid":61864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"一講到英文能力&hellip;真係高下立見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁當然如果你要用普通話能力做比較&hellip;<br />\n喺台灣讀書嘅大學生都有優勢嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：各有各好&hellip; 你係叻嘅讀咩大學都係一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"你諗太多啦<br />\n<br />\n而個社會限制得人最勁既就係背景"},{"pid":"d52d2b6c375604425d523adb561d62b953ab76b6","tid":611710,"uid":94454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 國際視野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97e8e12e5db0f322669512317db1eb2cb69fb6f","tid":611710,"uid":132296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"台灣出名係&quot;性&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你讀咩科，講埋聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1876eb424d9f1616f84dc5e940162492d4b47362","tid":611710,"uid":134779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"KongU仔當年鳩fingfing都fing到差唔多30分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1x分係弱智仔考"},{"pid":"c641f52cd7c77da5f533213213621cae472bd720","tid":611710,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc84d6c5d9f7ec508a280955c55b8633e57c2324","tid":611710,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"46292d0d0d35babb5da7907ef4adbe4205337456","tid":611710,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"廢就認"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n個班英美澳加撚<br />\n廢又唔認<br />\n真係好可憐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"見到你條友係到打飛機以為可以同英美澳加相比<br />\n真係好可悲"},{"pid":"7841585a827dae428794e3b10af9fb9efdfbff24","tid":611710,"uid":126269,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"咪又係睇u睇科<br />\n台灣一大堆廢u廢科係事實<br />\n正如外國都有成堆野雞u<br />\n只係出外國幾年英文起碼保到差極有限<br />\n<br />\n台灣讀好處大概係平同有得玩<br />\n仲有想升去美國搭路易啲<br />\n<br />\n不過喺台灣讀<br />\n一係就搵啲邊度讀都好打嘅科<br />\n一係就搵啲香港無/少嘅科<br />\n一係就搵啲比香港發展得好嘅科<br />\neg: <br />\n醫科：邊度讀都唔係話差太遠 因為開得醫資源都唔會少<br />\n獸醫：香港可以話近乎無 而且台灣係發展耐過香港<br />\npsy：本身香港對psy嘅體系根本係落後緊 只係cu搞得極好 其他u嘅psy根本就雞雞地 台灣psy體制完善 相比之下普遍發展比cu外嘅香港psy科好 即使廢到同香港psy差唔多嘅u都贏咗啲地方資源嘅優勢(intern/應用之類)<br />\n中文：只可以話同香港各有優勢<br />\n日文：以前台灣崇日所以發展得好<br />\n另外呢度堆例子見到 有幾科多數要用英文讀 所以都有返啲保底<br />\n<br />\n總括嚟講一樣係睇u睇科 只係多數都廢<br />\n<br />\n利伸：當初無要hku商科offer 走咗去台灣玩啲香港搞得廢嘅科 <br />\n<br />\nbtw台仔英文真心廢 除咗係少數非英文系又要英文讀嘅科 仲有台灣好多外地留學生"},{"pid":"10b2682cf9fa0c27a457caf763784da56b3998fb","tid":611710,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"印象中睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4fb85aaf9c7cf762fc6f2b361d9d61cd1c1242","tid":611710,"uid":135196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦，講咁多廢話<br />\n大家都係成績唔得先離開香港，但外國真係點都好聽啲，大家都係山雞大學冇人聽過，人地情願要個外國番嚟既，起碼英文好啲<br />\n國際視野？台灣人幾時有過？佢地既國際咪就係兩岸囉，真係好國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於能力同local u差唔多......呢項我就冇咩講，呢個包括好多方面，而其中的確台灣讀理工科既數理能力甚至會比local好，但讀大學既讀書能力並唔係重點，國際視野、學識學習技巧、培養交際技巧呢啲台灣就真係唔多得，成班到year3/4都仲好似小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁打打鬧鬧，讀書就淨係死背(工科喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n利申：係台北讀緊某間聲稱私立第一既學店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1acaf32dae5359c3e00c818e93816ff1c8df448","tid":611710,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"篇野好似好熟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba93a5ba30b2c3bd692d1ca3a36855dfba38a763","tid":611710,"uid":156370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如講吓你依家返緊咩工/做緊咩？"},{"pid":"2db0d2902992180cedc57a54a5d8b2de4cc732a